            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, at least one — a permanent brand hashtag like #NikeRun or #AsSeenOnMe. Campaign-specific hashtags are optional and only worth the effort if the campaign runs for 30+ days with a paid amplification budget.</p></div></div>
